===========

`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/connector-jira/issues/new?body=module:%20connector_jira_tempo%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.
